            <p>We built on RabbitMQ &mdash; a robust, performant and stable queue broker that everyone loves.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section id="quickstart">
    <div class="content">
      <h3 class="sectiontitle">It's as simple as 1-2-3.</h3>
      <div class="quickstart-steps">
        <div>1. Install</div>
        <pre><code class="lang-bash"><%= partial 'step_install' %></code></pre>
        <div>2. Make a Worker</div>
        <pre><code class="lang-ruby"><%= partial 'step_code' %></code></pre>
        <div>3. Run</div>
        <pre><code><%= partial 'step_run' %></code></pre>
